ISLAMABAD, Sep 01 (APP):National Disaster Management Authority (NDMA) has so far distributed 14,985 tents, 832.2 ton food and 2,956 blankets among flood hit people in collaboration with provincial relief agencies.
According to NDMA website, a total of 2,200 mosquito nets,2,350 plastic mats, 6,000 tarpaulins and 222 de watering pumps have so far been distributed among the flood hit peoples.
